rilli Nizza, Damiano Michieletto, Donato Di Gioia, Giacomo Puccini, Giovanna Lanza, Luca Casalin, Madama Butterfly, Massimiliano Pisapia, Opera lirica, Pinchas Steinberg, Teatro Regio di Torino"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/b41b40d04cc32e3e4f904f051c19deec" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Michele-Curnis-120x150.jpg" width="80" height="100" alt="Michele Curnis" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Michele Curnis"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/michele-curnis/">View all articles by Michele Curnis</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2014/02/ludwig-van-beethovenle-sinfonie-nr-5-in-do-minore-op-67/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Ludwig van Beethoven:Le Sinfonie (nr.5 in do minore op.67)</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2014/02/the-bravura-of-nose/" rel="next">The bravura of Nos. <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><div id="respond" class="comment-respon